releaseNotes:
#  (2024-06-17)


### Bug Fixes

* Adjust for spaces in nuget path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/827f03b9661c363c71910d3eb89534f08606c0a9)
* Adjust support for custom target frameworks (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/03b787c726ba931e72c17b1e4597035829eedae0)
* Adjust task version rename (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/9d795d1840da4b806e311fccf870df93ca0fc17a)
* Align linker version with ILLinkPack resolution (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/5caab463b429cf1f8804f832ae84d4a939c8224c)
* Correctly emit PWA manifest path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/cd7dc328fd8359046ab0e1e40886560c72c871f4)
* Disable service worker in debug to work around service workers interfering with browserlink (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/d46feb704dadedac96f71150a7f8015e896a924f)
* Don't define caps when the uno.sdk is present (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/1be69c7b236c4a5ea2389aa2d69d368d7a6486d5)
* Ensure that is included Microsoft.NET.ILLink.Tasks in 8.0.200 and later (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/02eec3e21bebb33ffc49b6b7d6fd564809452fa7)
* Link to data-formats documentation (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/b9683ccc268b0e36d70e0e00964c3a25eb356bc9)
* **macOS:** Don't link icalls to avoid using the cross-compiler (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/353744bb07cdd5436ab0e06cbb7116db32cbad76)
* More tuner fix for space in nuget path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/b5ad5cc3b9272555467640a19c7d9a2b51d4128c)
* remove double slash in path (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/bdfc3f7080ab4a9d1fc010f4ce70626c2659fdf0)
* Remove readonly attribute for output path deletion (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/72ea52dced653da108fb8d51057253206c4eb5e9)
* Restore clean target (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/02369db54509f7fe082cc327be9b5f891016d7a0)
* Set COEP/COOP headers when platform is not AnyCPU (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/2a49fc3e8b5b8021d100cd52df2cfb18f013f9e4)
* Specify root mode for root assembly (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/5cee302d7a8680fdcbe49803932f9e9475d18c46)
* Update runtime to latest (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/2372d16d9c25ee1fc9ccbe2c6bc7d568d7809a61)


### Features

* Support new Fingerprint and Integrity metadata required in .NET 9 SDK Preview 4 (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/23cedc7af65fe215d13d55c1e3ff451014264c84)


### Performance Improvements

* Fully disable prefetching (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/bc67d96e0b036962e1338f5ad68c1c581564e7ef)


### Reverts

* Revert "chore: Don't msbuild reuse nodes for windows testing" (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/f88924d565129f412e2d5961c32588784e49a6aa)
